'''Pete Heat''' (born Pete Hathway; 17 January 1983) is a UK-based [[Magic (illusion)|magician]] and television personality.

==Career==
Heat starred in the TV shows ''Around The World In 80 Tricks'' (Insight, 2016),<ref>http://www.insight.tv/#!/show/around-the-world-in-80-tricks/episode-8/episode-8</ref> ''Secrets Of The Brain'' (Insight, 2016)<ref>http://www.tvmole.com/2015/11/greenlit-secrets-of-the-brain-insight-tv/</ref> and ''Magic Party'' (BBC2NI, 2008).

He has also appeared at the [[Edinburgh Festival Fringe|Edinburgh Fringe]] with two shows, "The Magical Adventures Of Pete Heat" and "Miracles Etc".<ref>http://www.fringeguru.com/reviews/edinburgh-2012/the-magical-adventures-of-pete-heat.html</ref><ref>http://www.threeweeks.co.uk/article/ed2013-comedy-review-miracles-etc-pete-heat/</ref>

