[[Image:Stureplanmord, 2.jpg|220px|thumb|Sturecompagniet in March 2009]] '''Sturecompagniet''' is one of [[Sweden]]s biggest and most known nightclubs and is located at the old Sturebadets 1800-locals at Sturegatan 4 at [[Stureplan]] in [[Stockholm]].<ref>{{cite web|author=Senare Bilder Tidigare Bilder |url=http://stureplan.se/bilder/nattklubb/sturecompagniet |title=Sturecompagniet |publisher=Stureplan.Se |date= |accessdate=2014-02-18}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=Fredrik Jungstedt |url=http://whatsupsthlm.se/isthlm/sturecompagniet/46/ |title=Sturecompagniet » Klubb i Stockholm » Whatsupsthlm |publisher=Whatsupsthlm.se |date= |accessdate=2014-02-18}}</ref> Close to Sturecompagniet lies nightclubs Hell's Kitchen and IV.<ref>{{cite web|author=Sanna Björling |url=http://www.dn.se/diverse/p8-import-slask-pastan/stureplans-slutna-sallskap/ |title=Stureplans slutna sällskap |publisher=DN.SE |date=2006-05-10 |accessdate=2014-02-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140212115858/http://www.dn.se/diverse/p8-import-slask-pastan/stureplans-slutna-sallskap/ |archivedate=February 12, 2014 }}</ref> Sturecompagniet was in 1994 the scene of the notorious [[mass murder]] perpetrated by [[Tommy Zethraeus]].<ref>{{cite web|author=Anders Johansson |url=http://www.aftonbladet.se/nyheter/article18337613.ab |title=Zethraeus får tidsbestämt straff &#124; Nyheter &#124; Aftonbladet |publisher=Aftonbladet.se |date=2014-02-11 |accessdate=2014-02-18}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=Eric Tagesson |url=http://www.aftonbladet.se/nyheter/article16986534.ab |title=Stureplansmördare vill släppas fri &#124; Nyheter &#124; Aftonbladet |publisher=Aftonbladet.se |date=2013-06-19 |accessdate=2014-02-18}}</ref>
